      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable ride that won't break the bank? This vehicle is ready for its next chapter! While it shows some expected signs of use and cosmetic wear from its years of service, it remains a dependable choice that gets the job done. It's a great opportunity to own a functional, honest car at a very accessible price point!",
